            <h3>udit narayan</h3>
            <p>Udit Narayan Jha credited as Udit Narayan (born 1 December 1955)is an established Indian playback singer who works in Bollywood and whose songs have been featured mainly in Nepali and Bollywood movies. He has won three National Film Awards and five Filmfare Awards.</p>
